Pa 15:39 UTC pa Okutobala 4, 2021,<ref name="verge">{{cite web|url=https://www.theverge.com/2021/10/4/22709575/facebook-outage-instagram-whatsapp|title=Locked out and totally down: Facebook is scrambling to fix massive outage|work=The Verge|date=October 4, 2021|accessdate=October 4, 2021}}</ref> malo ochezera a ku [[United States|America]] a [[Facebook, Inc.|Facebook]] ndi othandizira ake, kuphatikiza [[Messenger]], Instagram, WhatsApp, [[Mapillary]], ndi [[Oculus]], adapezeka padziko lonse lapansi kwa maola opitilira asanu ndi awiri. Mapulogalamuwa atawonongeka, ogwiritsa ntchito adayamba kusamukira ku [[Twitter]], [[Discord]], ndi [[Telegraph]], zomwe zidapangitsa kusokonezeka kwa ma seva a mapulogalamuwa.<ref name="nyc">{{cite news|last1=Isaac|first1=Mike|last2=Frenkel|first2=Sheera|title=Facebook and all of its apps go down simultaneously.|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/10/04/technology/facebook-down.html|work=[[The New York Times]]|date=October 4, 2021}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=|title=Discord down? Current problems and outages|url=https://downdetector.com/status/discord/|url-status=live|access-date=4 October 2021|website=[[Downdetector]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211004205828/https://downdetector.com/status/discord/|archive-date=October 4, 2021}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Dewar|first=Caitlyn|date=4 October 2021|title=Is Twitter down?: Users report outage after Facebook, WhatsApp and Instagram go down|url=https://www.heraldscotland.com/news/19624807.twitter-users-report-outage-facebook-whatsapp-instagram-go/|access-date=4 October 2021|website=[[The Herald (Glasgow)|The Herald]]}}</ref> Kuzimaku kunayambitsidwa chifukwa cha kutayika kwa njira za IP kupita kuma seva a Facebook Domain Name (DNS), omwe onse anali odziyang'anira pawokha panthawiyo. Njira zapa Border Gateway Protocol (BGP) zidabwezeretsedwanso pazinthu zoyambira pafupifupi 20:50, ndipo ntchito za DNS zidayamba kupezeka nthawi ya 21:05 UTC, koma ntchito zosanjikiza zidabwezeredwa pang'onopang'ono pa [[Facebook]], [[Instagram]], ndi [[WhatsApp]] zambiri kuposa ola limodzi pambuyo pake, atatha kupitirira maola asanu ndi awiri.<ref>{{cite news|last1=Frenkel|first1=Sheera|title=Facebook coming back online after lengthy outage.|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/10/04/technology/facebook-back-online.html|access-date=4 October 2021|work=The New York Times}}</ref>

== Zoyambitsa ==
Akatswiri azachitetezo adazindikira kuti vutoli lidachotsedwa ngati Border Gateway Protocol (BGP) yochotsa ma adilesi a IP pomwe ma Domain Name Domain adasungidwa, zomwe zimapangitsa kuti ogwiritsa ntchito asamavutike kuthana ndi maina a Facebook ndi maina ena, ndikufikira ntchito. Zotsatira zake zidawonekera padziko lonse lapansi, mwachitsanzo wopereka chithandizo ku Internet ku Switzerland Init7 adalemba kutsika kwakukulu kwa intaneti pamasamba a Facebook pambuyo pa kusintha kwa Border Gateway Protocol.<ref>{{Cite web|title=Insta und WhatsApp down â€“ so stark schrumpfte der Internet-Traffic|url=https://www.watson.ch/!343713485|access-date=2021-10-04|website=watson.ch|language=de}}</ref>

Kentik ndi Cloudflare adanenanso kuti nthawi ya 15:39 UTC Facebook idapanga zosintha zingapo za BGP, kuphatikiza njira zopita kuzinthu zoyambirira za IP zomwe zimaphatikizira mayina awo onse ovomerezeka. Izi zidapangitsa kuti ma seva a Facebook a DNS asapezeke pa intaneti. Pofika 15:50 UTC, madera a Facebook anali atatha nthawi yayitali kuchokera pazosunga anthu onse. Kutatsala pang'ono kuti 21:00 UTC ipite, Facebook idayambiranso kulengeza zosintha za BGP, pomwe dzina la Facebook lidayambiranso pa 21:05 UTC.<ref name="cloudflarepostmortem">{{cite web|title=Understanding How Facebook Disappeared from the Internet|first1=Tom|last1=Strickx|first2=Celso|last2=Martinho|url=https://blog.cloudflare.com/october-2021-facebook-outage/|date=4 October 2021|access-date=4 October 2021}}</ref>

Pafupifupi 22:45 UTC, Facebook ndi ntchito zokhudzana nazo zimapezeka nthawi zambiri.<ref>{{Cite news|date=2021-10-04|title=Facebook, Whatsapp and Instagram back after outage|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/technology-58793174|access-date=2021-10-04}}</ref>

== Yankho ==
Chief Technology Officer wa Facebook a [[Mike Schroepfer]] adalemba kupepesa patatha nthawi yopumula mpaka maola angapo, akunena kuti, "Matimu akugwira ntchito mwachangu momwe angathetsere ndikubwezeretsa mwachangu momwe angathere."<ref name="indy">{{cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/gadgets-and-tech/twitter-down-outage-not-working-b1932250.html|title=Twitter users suggest site is slowing down as it takes pressure from Facebook and Instagram outage|newspaper=The Independent|date=October 4, 2021|accessdate=October 4, 2021}}</ref>

Woimira ku America a Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez adatumiza mawu pa tsambali, ndikupempha anthu kuti agawane "nkhani zofotokoza" pa Twitter, akunyoza mbiri ya Facebook pofalitsa zomwe zili zokayikitsa. Twitter ndi Reddit adayikiranso ma tweets pamaakaunti awo a Twitter omwe amanyoza kutuluka.<ref name="BBC">{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-58793174|title=Facebook, Whatsapp and Instagram suffer outage|work=BBC News|date=October 4, 2021|accessdate=October 4, 2021}}</ref>

Ogwiritsa ntchito onse a Twitter ndi Telegalamu adanenanso zakuchedwa munthawi zoyankha, zomwe zimakhulupirira kuti zimayambitsidwa ndi anthu nthawi zambiri pa Facebook omwe amasinthana nawo.<ref name="indy2">{{cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/gadgets-and-tech/twitter-down-outage-not-working-b1932250.html|title=Twitter users suggest site is slowing down as it takes pressure from Facebook and Instagram outage|newspaper=The Independent|date=October 4, 2021|accessdate=October 4, 2021}}</ref>

